Package: BayesR
Title: Bayesian Estimation of Hierarchical Generalized Structured Additive Regression Models
Version: 0.1-1
Date: 2010-08-20
Author: Stefan Lang, Nikolaus Umlauf
Maintainer: Nikolaus Umlauf <nikolaus.umlauf@uibk.ac.at>
Depends: R (>= 2.10.1)
Description: Routine for the estimation of Bayesian hierarchical generalized structured additive regression models 
	     with MCMC Gibbs sampling, including optimal hyperparameter estimation.
Depends: colorspace, fields, geometry, msm, mgcv, akima
LazyLoad: yes
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
